{"tid":464621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★天氣太冷會導致 iPhone X 觸控操作失靈","createTime":"2017-11-10T16:36:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-11T04:13:56.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a8d763126bfe4cb0fb76036cf01a0edd5f05da78","tid":464621,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T16:36:31.000Z","msg":"蘋果公司在<span style=\"color: red;\">本周四確認了有關 iPhone X 在寒冷環境下觸摸功能失靈的問題</span>。蘋果的一位發言人稱，當手機迅速進入寒冷環境后，iPhone X 的屏幕會暫時喪失對觸摸的反應，不過會在幾秒鐘后恢復。這位發言人還表示，他們準備在接下來的軟件更新中解決這個問題，但是他並沒有說明這一補丁具體會在什麼時間推出。<br />\n<br />\n在 Reddit 社區 里，稱自己遇到同樣問題的人似乎也有不少。實際上，類似問題在蘋果以前的機型中也曾出現過<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hksilicon.com/articles/1472817\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hksilicon.com%2Farticles%2F1472817&d=v7tCjXvSgzELQr0%2BGK7bPMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=64afe90e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hksilicon.com/articles/1472817</a>"},{"pid":"18b3f28a4d785e20bfd5331468825369737b45ab","tid":464621,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T16:37:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a22a1601d3f8584c2fc48254cff8700663ff1f","tid":464621,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T16:38:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但是他並沒有說明這一補丁具體會在什麼時間推出</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nnone can fix<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"003cefaaeea8f1aef34996231b575d36a3a6a4cb","tid":464621,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T16:40:22.000Z","msg":"Apple IT meeting<img src=\"/assets/fac